# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Studio Prime — repository ignore rules
# This repo ships PROMPTS. The files below are either runtime state
# that Studio Prime generates inside *target* projects, secrets, or
# internal scaffolding that must never enter the public repo.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Studio Prime runtime state (generated in the projects the agent builds — never committed here)
.studio/
.tmp/
architecture/phase_snapshots/
design-system/MASTER.md

# Secrets & environment
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key

# Internal scaffolding / process docs (kept out of the public repo)
claude.md
gemini.md
findings.md
progress.md
task_plan.md
check_hardening*.ps1
evolution.zip

# Dependencies & build output (for any example projects)
node_modules/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
dist/
build/
target/
coverage/

# OS & editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
